      <h1 class="am-title">Four Days at the<br>Top of Michigan</h1>
      <div class="am-meta">
        <span class="am-pill">Jun 13–17</span>
        <span class="am-pill">St. Ignace</span>
        <span class="am-pill">6 travelers</span>
